                    <span>This book is a must for every web developer, although I think it's time for a newer version, as some of the examples and theories are based on pre-2000 studies.<p>Overall you can expect a great insight on correct web-design, colors matching, liquid pages, use of navigation and quick respond to user needs.</span>
                  
